quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Ngifunga ngelanga nokucwazimula kwalo
  91,2,Futhi ngifunga ngenyanga uma ililandela (ilanga)
  91,3,Futhi ngifunga ngemini uma ivela
  91,4,Futhi ngifunga ngobusuku uma buyimboza
  91,5,Futhi ngifunga ngesibhakabhaka kanye nalowo owasakha
  91,6,Futhi ngifunga ngomhlaba kanye nalowo owawendlala
  91,7,"Futhi\tngifunga\tngomphefumulo\tkanye\tnalowo owawulinganisa"
  91,8,Wasewukhombisa okubi kwawo kanye nokuhle kwawo
  91,9,Ngempela uphumelele lowo owuhlanzile (umphefumulo wakhe)
  91,10,Futhi ngempela wehlulekile lowo owenze okubi kuwona
  91,11,"(Abantu)\tbaThamud\tbaphika\t(umphrofethi\twabo) ngokungahloniphi"
  91,12,Ngenkathi lowo oyisoni kubona eya phambili
  91,13,"Manjalo sabe sesithi isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi kubona, “Ningalithinti, yikameli lensikazi likaMvelinqangi nesiphuzo salo”"
  91,14,"Ngakho-ke basiphika (isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi) balibulala, manjalo iNkosi yabo yehlisela phezulu kwabo imbubhiso ngenxa yesono sabo yasilinganisa (kubona bonke)"
  91,15,Futhi ayiwesabi umphumela walokho